597
00:29:47,458 --> 00:29:49,791
So, what does it mean
that Seamus wanted to marry Fiona?

598
00:29:49,875 --> 00:29:51,125
It's Shakespeare.

599
00:29:51,208 --> 00:29:54,583
Two brothers smuggling drugs,
fighting for control of their empire.

