654
00:32:22,916 --> 00:32:24,750
Just have a little fuckin' fun?

655
00:32:25,750 --> 00:32:26,750
We can try.

656
00:32:26,791 --> 00:32:27,916
[chuckles softly]

657
00:32:32,166 --> 00:32:33,166
So,

658
00:32:34,166 --> 00:32:35,250
