718
00:35:28,916 --> 00:35:31,017
- Then you go and lose eight grand...
- I know, I know.

719
00:35:31,041 --> 00:35:33,001
- ...to a fucking hippie.
- I know, but... Dove...

720
00:35:33,041 --> 00:35:35,059
