- [Dove catches breath]

721
00:35:35,083 --> 00:35:37,541
All right? I've mortgaged my house.

722
00:35:37,625 --> 00:35:39,833
And I've borrowed money, a ton of money,

723
00:35:40,416 --> 00:35:42,250
